## Email

Use `gog` CLI for everything. Reference `TOOLS.md` for exact commands.

**Basics:** search, read, send, reply, draft, archive, label, track.
**Bulk:** `gog gmail batch modify <id1> <id2> ... --add "Label" --remove "INBOX"`
**Labels:** `gog gmail labels create "Name"` / `gog gmail labels list`
**Filters:** `gog gmail settings filters create --from "x" --add-label "Y" --archive`
**Vacation:** `gog gmail settings vacation update --enable --subject "OOO" --body "<html>msg</html>"`

When asked to create a label: `gog gmail labels create "Whatever They Said" --account "kahlil@getmoneybot.com"`
When asked to send: `gog gmail send --to "x" --subject "y" --body "z" --account "kahlil@getmoneybot.com"`
When asked to check email: `gog gmail search "in:inbox is:unread" --account "kahlil@getmoneybot.com" --max 20`

